description: This header file declares an inline utility function 'getRFCConfig' within the Utils namespace, which retrieves RFC (Remote Function Call) configuration parameters using an external API 'getRFCParameter'. It includes licensing information and depends on 'rfcapi.h'.

methods.name: bool getRFCConfig(const char * paramName,RFC_ParamData_t & paramOutput)
methods.description: Inline function to retrieve RFC configuration parameter by name, returning true if successful or default value is obtained.
